CSS: cascading style sheet
-> there are 3 types to apply css in html web pages

1) inline CSS
2) internal CSS
3) external CSS
--------------------------
1) inline css: 
-> apply css on specific elements its called inline CSS

    syntax:
        <h1 style= "propertys: value"></h1>

2) internal css:
-> it is apply on spacific web pages

    <style>......css goes hear</style>

3) external css:
-> this is usfull for whole project we can apply external project we can apply external scc on full web
    page creation external css web page and connect with <link> elements

