selectors:
1) element selectore:
-> apply css element wise
    e.g.
        h1
        {
                propertys:value
        }

2) group selectore:
-> to apply same style same css on specific group of elements
        e.g.
        h1,h3
        {
            propertys: values
        }

3) class selectore :
-> to apply specific class on specific element class selector denoted by (.) peretor

        e.g
            .myclass
            {

            }

4) id selectore:
-> to represent unique style for specific element we can use id selectore
-> id selector represent by (#)

            e.g.
                #myid
                {

                }

5) universal selector :
-> universal selectore represent by (*)

                e.g.
                    *
                    {
                        
                    }